cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use FedAgent in your research, please cite it as below."
title: "FedAgent: Federated Agent Reinforcement Learning"
abstract: >-
  A decentralized reinforcement-learning framework for collaboratively training
  LLM agents across distributed clients without sharing local data, with a
  two-level (task vs. environment) heterogeneity taxonomy and an asymmetric
  robustness analysis.
type: software
